  <metadata>
    <name>Tour3d 01, Day 3: Höllental &amp; Kinzigtal Home</name>
    <desc>From Staufen, ride through Freiburg and up the dramatic Höllental gorge. Continue through Hinterzarten and the Elztal north to Wolfach and Gengenbach. Return via Oberkirch and Baden-Baden.</desc>
  </metadata>
